， <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-killers-tickets%2Fartist%2F926809" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可在此处购买</a>。</p><p><strong>六月</strong><br /><strong>星期五 14 – 六月 都柏林, 3Arena</strong><br /><strong>星期六 15 – 都柏林，3Arena</strong><br /> <strong>18 日星期二 – 曼彻斯特，Co-Op Live</strong><br /><strong>周三 19 日 – 曼彻斯特，Co-Op Live</strong><br /><strong>星期五 21 – 曼彻斯特，Co-Op Live</strong><br /><strong>星期二 25 – 格拉斯哥，Ovo Hydro</strong><br /><strong>周三 26 日 – 格拉斯哥，Ovo Hydro</strong><br /><strong>七月</strong><br /><strong>星期四 4 – 7 月 伦敦，O2</strong><br /><strong>星期五 5 – 伦敦，O2</strong><br /><strong>周日 7 – 伦敦，O2</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3489144" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3489144" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3489144" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-killers-reading@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2023 年雷丁杀手队。图片来源：Chris Phelps" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-killers-reading@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-killers-reading@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-killers-reading@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-killers-reading@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-killers-reading@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-killers-reading@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3489144" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年雷丁杀手队。图片来源：Chris Phelps</figcaption></figure><p>这次巡演将庆祝乐队的全部唱片，从他们开创性的首张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-7438-307071">Hot Fuss</a> ”（2004年）到“Sam&#39;s Town”（2006年）、“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-killers-10008-341913"